Question: Could you fetch the year-to-date earnings for Robert Thorne (EMP-7721) for the 2025 fiscal year?
Call: { "func_call": "get_ytd_earnings", "employee_id": "EMP-7721", "period": "2025-FY" }
Response: { "employee_id": "EMP-7721", "period": "2025-FY", "gross": 92300.00, "deductions": 21450.25, "net": 70849.75, "currency": "USD" }

